accessibility.text: Contributions made by Ramanujan in the field of mathematics
Here is a list of some of the notable contributions made by Ramanujan:
Discovery of the Ramanujan theta function (1913)

Ramanujan made many other contributions to mathematics during his career, which spanned from around 1913 to 1920. He is considered one of the greatest mathematicians in history, and his work has had a lasting impact on the field.
